## Git hooks（可选）

详细说明与策略：[`.cursor/references/rules/git-hooks.md`](.cursor/references/rules/git-hooks.md)

```bash
bash setup-hooks.sh
bash setup-hooks.sh --force
bash setup-hooks.sh -h
```
